title: Bump tokio-rustls to 0.24 to ensure dependency convergence
body:
`tokio-rustls 0.23` depends on `rustls = 0.20`, which conflicts with `rustls = 0.21` requirement.

This change bumps the `tokio-rustls` to 0.24. `tokio-rustls` no longer re-exports `webpki`, so this change adds `webpki` as a dependency as well.

title: Ensure client is authenticated before switching to RESP3
body:
If not done so, the following error will happen (if password is
required):

```
NOAUTH HELLO must be called with the client already authenticated,
otherwise the HELLO AUTH <user> <pass> option can be used to
authenticate the client and select the RESP protocol version at the same
time
```

Closes #54
